么挣，也不用问挣来干什么用，到死的时候像葛朗台一样抱着一堆金币说：啊，真暖和啊……所以，美妙人生的关键在于你能迷上什么东西。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"-uG26Sv8\"\u003e和《赤壁赋》中，客人“哀吾生之须臾，羡长江之无穷。”时，苏轼所讲“客亦知夫水与月乎？逝者如斯，而未尝往也；盈虚者如彼，而卒莫消长也。盖将自其变者而观之，则天地曾不能以一瞬；自其不变者而观之，则物与我皆无尽也，而又何羡乎!”有异曲同工之妙。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"dMQa0npd\"\u003e所以啊，吾生也有涯，而知也无涯。以有涯随无涯，殆已!重要的是找到让自己着迷的东西，填满自己的内心世界，让自己的一生充实就不算庸碌。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"KLNGuvu-\"\u003e更\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"ewfjRMXN\"\u003e现在社会的生产力条件决定有得必有舍，但是找一个心灵的寄托，填满自己的内心世界并不难啊。大刘和苏轼的思想是没错的，毕竟社会总是要求思想先行发展的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"is_thanked":false,"is_nothelp":false,"voting":0},"is_labeled":false,"visited_count":243648,"favorite_count":1825,"answer_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"type\": \"answer\", \"id\": 3267427989}","attached_info":"","action_card":false},{"id":"147_1750980680.727","type":"feed","offset":147,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1750980680,"updated_time":1750980680,"target":{"id":"404664608","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/404664608","author":{"id":"b569149131b374bdf64dbbcbea80c280","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/b569149131b374bdf64dbbcbea80c280","user_type":"people","url_token":"gao-leng-leng-61","name":"高冷冷","headline":"可以去公众号「高冷冷」认识我","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/06b639a747310f990dba12ee1c0b638a_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"gender":0,"followers_count":783688,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false},"created_time":1527605513,"updated_time":1589269007,"voteup_count":86807,"thanks_count":46179,"comment_count":1696,"is_copyable":false,"question":{"id":"33453309","type":"question","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/33453309","author":{"id":"a7f27bba2ca98eccfb23bef54e4ea2d8","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/a7f27bba2ca98eccfb23bef54e4ea2d8","user_type":"people","url_token":"you-le-26","name":"由乐","headline":"财务管理","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/0fe4388ff81a9b605029263b1f376de2_l